          "text": "The user is asking about how to pass a string to a function in C++ - by pointer, reference, or value. This is a conceptual question, not an edit request. I can answer without making any changes.\n\nThey want to extract the while-loop cleanup logic (trimming trailing \\r and spaces from the input string, like in task 1's code) into a separate function.",
