e trimmed version.\n\nActually, I think combining into one function IS fine for this scale. The function \"trim and tell me if it's only whitespace\" is a natural operation. But if we need the trimmed result, we also need a way to get it back.\n\nLet me just present both options with trade-offs and let the user decide.",
